1
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:11,610
Is it delicious?

2
00:02:12,710 --> 00:02:14,590
How about you eat first?

3
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:16,520
No.

4
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:18,030
Mo, you should eat first.

5
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:20,310
I want to sit on my favorite swing,

6
00:02:20,310 --> 00:02:22,430
eating my favorite candied hawthorns.

7
00:02:22,430 --> 00:02:22,870
Okay.

8
00:02:23,310 --> 00:02:23,840
Let's go.

9
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:13,400
Uncle Lie.

10
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,240
Father.

11
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:18,280
Uncle Lie, what happened to your leg?

12
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,560
Go, quickly.

13
00:03:20,190 --> 00:03:20,680
Hurry.

14
00:03:21,079 --> 00:03:22,540
Let's climb over the wall.

15
00:03:33,030 --> 00:03:33,680
Han Mo.

16
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:36,000
Yunling, I'm scared.

17
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:37,800
Han Mo.

18
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:42,240
Han Mo! Han Mo!

19
00:04:10,630 --> 00:04:12,070
General Xiao, you're carrying the badge
bestowed by His Majesty

20
00:04:12,070 --> 00:04:13,520
to enter the Imperial Prison.

21
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,450
I can't stop you.

22
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,240
But,

23
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,920
as for Han Mo's case,

24
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:19,000
I think you'd better not look into it.

25
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:19,800
Why?

26
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:22,240
Is it possible that Han Mo's case file

27
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,870
has something fishy about it?

28
00:04:23,870 --> 00:04:24,720
Absolutely not.

29
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:26,250
It's just that this case...

30
00:04:36,190 --> 00:04:37,630
Take me to see Han Mo right now.

31
00:04:37,630 --> 00:04:39,270
He is a heavily punished criminal here.

32
00:04:39,270 --> 00:04:40,600
Without His Majesty's decree,

33
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,600
you cannot see him.

34
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:42,430
What?

35
00:04:43,070 --> 00:04:45,530
This doesn't count
as His Majesty's decree?

36
00:04:45,680 --> 00:04:46,870
It counts.

37
00:04:47,390 --> 00:04:48,920
General Xiao, please come this way.

38
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:50,120
I'll take you there.

39
00:04:54,270 --> 00:04:55,600
General Xiao, this way.

40
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:06,630
General Xiao.

41
00:05:06,630 --> 00:05:08,120
He is the most special prisoner here.

42
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,360
I was ordered to keep him strung up

43
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,310
upside down during the day

44
00:05:10,310 --> 00:05:11,770
and take him down at night.

45
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:13,600
When I became
the Ministry of Justice's historian,

46
00:05:13,600 --> 00:05:15,070
the previous historian
instructed me to do so.

47
00:05:15,070 --> 00:05:17,240
It has been done for many years.

48
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:19,870
Are you Han Mo?

49
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:23,390
Han Mo.

50
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,360
Han Mo.

51
00:05:39,950 --> 00:05:40,750
Han Yunling.

52
00:05:41,510 --> 00:05:42,310
Han Yunling.

53
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:44,920
Han Yunling.

54
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:52,920
What are you doing
in the middle of the night?

55
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:54,070
Come with me right now.

56
00:05:54,070 --> 00:05:55,070
Han Mo is dying.

57
00:06:22,510 --> 00:06:24,680
I'll go outside
and guard the main door for you.

58
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,390
Okay.

59
00:06:58,270 --> 00:07:00,240
Thank you for helping me find my cousin.

60
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,360
As long as it's him.

61
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:03,240
Take a look quickly.

62
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:07,680
Mo.

63
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:09,600
Mo.

64
00:07:17,190 --> 00:07:18,000
Here.

65
00:07:32,310 --> 00:07:33,120
Mo.

66
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:36,600
You are?

67
00:07:36,950 --> 00:07:38,270
I am your cousin.

68
00:07:38,870 --> 00:07:40,120
I'm here to save you.

69
00:07:41,830 --> 00:07:42,870
Yunling.

70
00:07:47,510 --> 00:07:49,390
Save me.

71
00:07:52,310 --> 00:07:53,120
Mo.

72
00:07:54,270 --> 00:07:55,470
What happened to him?

73
00:08:06,510 --> 00:08:08,870
He is already dead.

74
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,600
Oh, Chief Shen.

75
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,600
Why didn't you

76
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:21,630
have someone inform us
in advance before you came?

77
00:08:21,630 --> 00:08:22,190
What?

78
00:08:22,190 --> 00:08:24,720
Do I have to report to you
when I visit the Imperial Prison?

79
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:25,310
That's not what I meant.

80
00:08:25,310 --> 00:08:26,390
You are the Chief.

81
00:08:26,390 --> 00:08:28,270
Who can stop you, right?

82
00:08:28,270 --> 00:08:29,630
Cut the crap.

83
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,830
Lord Zhang is in a bad mood today.

84
00:08:34,789 --> 00:08:35,909
Chief.

85
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:38,750
Hurry up and leave.

86
00:08:38,750 --> 00:08:39,809
Someone is coming.

87
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:41,120
Don't get caught.

88
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:42,840
No.

89
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:03,270
Why are you dawdling?

90
00:09:03,270 --> 00:09:04,000
You guard the prison,

91
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:05,530
and you can't find the keys?

92
00:09:09,870 --> 00:09:11,720
You old fart,

93
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:12,670
why don't you carry

94
00:09:12,670 --> 00:09:13,510
such important things with you?

95
00:09:13,510 --> 00:09:14,080
You're right.

96
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,120
I'm telling you,

97
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:16,630
if he gets away,

98
00:09:16,790 --> 00:09:18,270
Lord Zhang will kill your whole family.

99
00:09:18,270 --> 00:09:18,750
I know.

100
00:09:19,790 --> 00:09:20,870
Lord Zhang.

101
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:22,870
Which Lord Zhang?

102
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,600
Go away.

103
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:36,320
As usual, lock the door and get lost.

104
00:09:36,320 --> 00:09:37,790
Come back

105
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,120
when we're done.

106
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:39,750
Yes.

107
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,270
So quiet.

108
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:47,030
Playing dead?

109
00:09:47,390 --> 00:09:49,440
It's useless to play dead today.

110
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,600
You can't escape

111
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:51,910
this torture.

112
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,360
Beat him!

113
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,120
Yes.

114
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:59,320
Playing dead, huh?

115
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:00,000
Fine.

116
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:02,080
Watch me beat you to death.

117
00:10:03,030 --> 00:10:03,870
Pretend.

118
00:10:04,390 --> 00:10:05,390
Keep pretending.

119
00:10:05,390 --> 00:10:06,390
Playing dead?

120
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:10,120
They won't even spare Mo's corpse.

121
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:11,480
I'll fight them!

122
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:13,240
Playing dead?

123
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,270
Calm down now.

124
00:10:16,670 --> 00:10:17,670
Calm down.

125
00:10:18,870 --> 00:10:20,200
Beat him to death!

126
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:21,150
Beat him!

127
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:25,360
They even humiliate Mo's corpse.

128
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,200
What kind of deep hatred

129
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,870
do the Hans have against them

130
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:28,600
that they won't even

131
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:30,200
spare a dead man's corpse?

132
00:10:31,910 --> 00:10:32,440
Actually,

133
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:34,670
I've always felt that Han Mo's case

134
00:10:34,670 --> 00:10:35,550
is fishy.

135
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:37,480
He was locked up
in the Imperial Prison alone

136
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,910
for more than a decade.

137
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,390
Tortured every day,

138
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,510
yet kept alive.

139
00:10:42,390 --> 00:10:43,670
If it wasn't a deep hatred,

140
00:10:43,670 --> 00:10:44,910
there was no need for this.

141
00:10:44,910 --> 00:10:45,510
Moreover,

142
00:10:46,030 --> 00:10:47,360
I checked his case file.

143
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:49,200
It's completely blank.

144
00:10:49,630 --> 00:10:50,490
Think about it.

145
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:53,790
Who exactly persecuted
the Han family back then?

146
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:56,520
Leave no survivors!

147
00:11:02,270 --> 00:11:04,130
Forget what should be forgotten.

148
00:11:04,510 --> 00:11:05,910
Live well.

149
00:11:10,510 --> 00:11:12,150
I injured my head at the time

150
00:11:12,150 --> 00:11:13,720
and don't remember many things.

151
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:15,600
Uncle Lie rarely mentioned it either.

152
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:17,390
Later, whenever I asked him about it,

153
00:11:17,390 --> 00:11:19,200
he always said it was in the past,

154
00:11:19,440 --> 00:11:21,300
and told us to live in the present.

155
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:23,450
Don't worry,

156
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,080
I'm here.

157
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,840
I will find out the truth for you.

158
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:34,410
But I have one more presumptuous request.

159
00:11:34,910 --> 00:11:35,720
Tell me.

160
00:11:37,910 --> 00:11:40,240
Can you give me Mo's body?

161
00:11:40,270 --> 00:11:43,530
I want to take him back to Changmo
to reunite with Uncle Lie.

162
00:11:43,790 --> 00:11:45,030
About the body...

163
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:51,960
About the body,

164
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:53,800
I will figure something out.

165
00:11:59,670 --> 00:12:02,070
You haven't been treated for several days.

166
00:12:02,670 --> 00:12:04,600
Let me give you acupuncture first.

167
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:06,390
Let's skip it today.

168
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:07,550
Get some good rest.

169
00:12:08,270 --> 00:12:10,270
I'll go figure something out first.

170
00:12:16,750 --> 00:12:18,320
Lord Li,

171
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:21,630
give me a reply.

172
00:12:22,150 --> 00:12:23,720
Oh, Lord Wang,

173
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,480
calm down.

174
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:28,510
His Majesty told you to stay home
without any duties.

175
00:12:28,510 --> 00:12:29,910
He didn't say anything against you.

176
00:12:29,910 --> 00:12:31,320
He hasn't charged you with anything.

177
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:32,910
Why are you panicking?

178
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:34,750
Besides,

179
00:12:34,750 --> 00:12:35,810
about this matter,

180
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:39,320
why don't you go to Lord Zhang?

181
00:12:39,510 --> 00:12:41,080
Ah, Lord Zhang.

182
00:12:41,080 --> 00:12:43,440
He is extremely rigid.

183
00:12:43,600 --> 00:12:44,360
Moreover,

184
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:45,870
would he

185
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:47,320
go to His Majesty

186
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:49,270
and humbly plead for me?

187
00:12:49,270 --> 00:12:52,030
Well, just beg him.

188
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:54,000
You and he are both
among the 3 Chief Ministers.

189
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:56,510
He will give you some face.

190
00:12:56,510 --> 00:12:58,390
Forget it.

191
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:00,910
Then I have no other way.

192
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,030
You, this...

193
00:13:02,030 --> 00:13:02,510
I...

194
00:13:03,510 --> 00:13:06,320
I've already sent back the Desert Realm

195
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:08,480
dancers you gave me.

196
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:11,720
Please think of a way for me.

197
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,000
Lord Wang.

198
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:15,120
Am I that kind of person?

199
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:17,200
I gave them to you fair and square.

200
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:19,000
How can I just take them back now?

201
00:13:22,840 --> 00:13:24,150
I have no other choice.

202
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:26,080
How about

203
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:31,240
I take you alone to the palace...

204
00:13:32,270 --> 00:13:33,600
To meet His Majesty?

205
00:13:36,270 --> 00:13:37,870
That would be great.

206
00:13:40,390 --> 00:13:42,270
Let's go right now.

207
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:43,630
Lord Wang.

208
00:13:43,630 --> 00:13:44,510
Wait, wait.

209
00:13:44,510 --> 00:13:45,510
Don't rush, don't rush.

210
00:13:45,510 --> 00:13:46,670
Lord Wang, look,

211
00:13:46,670 --> 00:13:49,440
how is my calligraphy?

212
00:13:49,750 --> 00:13:51,840
Riding on the crest of success.

213
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:57,120
Yes, riding on the crest of success.

214
00:14:03,790 --> 00:14:06,320
Stories from ancient times
are fascinating.

215
00:14:06,790 --> 00:14:09,790
The 3 sworn brothers swore
an oath in the Peach Garden,

216
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:11,670
set out to shape the fate of the realm,

217
00:14:11,670 --> 00:14:13,200
and achieved great things.

218
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:14,510
Right, Lord Li?

219
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:18,910
Coming to see me today,

220
00:14:19,270 --> 00:14:20,360
what is the matter?

221
00:14:20,670 --> 00:14:22,120
Your Majesty.

222
00:14:22,440 --> 00:14:24,510
Previously in the court,

223
00:14:24,510 --> 00:14:26,510
didn't Your Majesty,
in front of all officials,

224
00:14:26,510 --> 00:14:28,630
ask Lord Wang go home for a vacation?

225
00:14:29,240 --> 00:14:31,910
I don't think this is enough.

226
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:33,360
He is guilty,

227
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:34,690
and he must be punished.

228
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:36,440
So today,

229
00:14:36,440 --> 00:14:40,240
I brought Wang Ruhai here
to see Your Majesty.

230
00:14:40,910 --> 00:14:42,840
It's so hot outside.

231
00:14:43,240 --> 00:14:45,100
Are you just going to let Lord Wang

232
00:14:45,670 --> 00:14:46,550
kneel outside like this?

233
00:14:46,550 --> 00:14:48,390
Your Majesty is absolutely right.

234
00:14:48,390 --> 00:14:50,720
But Wang Ruhai has
committed heinous crimes.

235
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:53,840
Being punished in front of Your Majesty

236
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:55,910
is his good fortune.

237
00:14:55,910 --> 00:14:56,440
All right.

238
00:14:56,440 --> 00:14:58,870
Tell Wang Ruhai to stop kneeling.

239
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:00,600
He is getting old.

240
00:15:00,910 --> 00:15:02,770
Don't let him kneel himself sick.

241
00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:06,320
But about Wang Ruhai
staying at home idly...

242
00:15:08,390 --> 00:15:10,960
I punished him in front of

243
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:12,440
so many civil and military officials.

244
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:14,440
Can he be forgiven just by kneeling?

245
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:16,860
Where would the law of the land be?

246
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:18,720
And where would my authority be?

247
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:19,910
Right, right.

248
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:22,080
That's exactly what I told Wang Ruhai.

249
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:25,080
But he's counting on
his merits in assisting the court.

250
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:27,910
He also said he's willing
to accept punishment

251
00:15:27,910 --> 00:15:29,200
and kneel of his own accord.

252
00:15:29,200 --> 00:15:31,930
And if Your Majesty still
refuses to forgive him,

253
00:15:31,960 --> 00:15:32,870
he will...

254
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:33,860
He will do what?

255
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:37,240
It is inconvenient for me to say.

256
00:15:38,790 --> 00:15:41,080
If it's inconvenient, then don't say it.

257
00:15:41,910 --> 00:15:42,910
Tell him for me.

258
00:15:43,630 --> 00:15:45,120
I am a wise ruler.

259
00:15:45,630 --> 00:15:47,120
Before finding out the truth,

260
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:49,200
I will not add more punishment to him.

261
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:50,240
Let him go home

262
00:15:50,630 --> 00:15:52,160
and stay there peacefully.

263
00:15:52,270 --> 00:15:54,240
Thank you, Your Majesty.

264
00:15:54,240 --> 00:15:56,030
I will take my leave.

265
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:05,390
What did His Majesty say?

266
00:16:05,390 --> 00:16:07,440
-Lord Wang.
-Tell me quickly.

267
00:16:07,510 --> 00:16:10,720
Alas, what could His Majesty say?

268
00:16:11,030 --> 00:16:12,000
His Majesty is

269
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:15,480
still angry with you.

270
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:18,390
If I hadn't pleaded for you in person,

271
00:16:18,550 --> 00:16:20,480
His Majesty would have
made you kneel here all day.

272
00:16:20,480 --> 00:16:21,510
Kneel all...

273
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:23,200
This kid...

274
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:27,670
I am, after all, a regent entrusted
by the late emperor.

275
00:16:27,670 --> 00:16:29,720
I have already kneeled to apologize,

276
00:16:29,720 --> 00:16:32,910
b-but he is still indifferent.

277
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:33,670
No.

278
00:16:34,030 --> 00:16:36,080
I have to reason with him face to face.

279
00:16:36,080 --> 00:16:36,840
You can't do that.

280
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:38,320
Don't stop me.

281
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:39,200
Lord Wang.

282
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:42,200
I have said all the good words.

283
00:16:42,200 --> 00:16:45,000
But His Majesty is in a bad mood.

284
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:47,030
Let's go back and think it over.

285
00:16:47,030 --> 00:16:48,510
Let me tell you...

286
00:16:48,510 --> 00:16:49,390
My back, my legs,

287
00:16:49,390 --> 00:16:50,910
even my tailbone are all shot.

288
00:16:50,910 --> 00:16:52,790
Otherwise, I would have
gone to reason with him long ago.

289
00:16:52,790 --> 00:16:54,320
Slow down.

290
00:16:55,630 --> 00:16:56,870
At Tianlang Pass,

291
00:16:56,870 --> 00:16:58,480
I treated you well.

292
00:16:58,630 --> 00:16:59,870
Now that we are in your territory,

293
00:16:59,870 --> 00:17:01,440
you should treat me well.

294
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:04,240
I'll make sure there's
plenty of good wine for you.

295
00:17:04,240 --> 00:17:04,770
Let's go.

296
00:17:23,720 --> 00:17:24,980
What's wrong with you?

297
00:17:29,240 --> 00:17:30,030
Nothing.

298
00:17:32,270 --> 00:17:34,400
No one saw you when you came, right?

299
00:17:34,510 --> 00:17:35,000
No.

300
00:17:35,680 --> 00:17:36,410
That's good.

301
00:17:37,240 --> 00:17:38,240
I've brought him.

302
00:17:53,310 --> 00:17:54,110
Mo.

303
00:17:55,720 --> 00:17:57,270
Mo, I'm sorry.

304
00:17:58,270 --> 00:17:59,920
I'm late.

305
00:17:59,920 --> 00:18:02,480
Mo, I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

306
00:18:07,510 --> 00:18:08,640
Don't be afraid, Mo.

307
00:18:09,590 --> 00:18:11,000
I will take you home.

308
00:18:27,510 --> 00:18:28,680
Mo is not dead.

309
00:18:31,070 --> 00:18:32,670
I saw it in Uncle Lie's notes.

310
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:35,510
As long as we drive silver needles
through the major meridians

311
00:18:35,510 --> 00:18:37,040
and give him a Revival Pill,

312
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:39,600
if he isn't completely gone,

313
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:41,660
he won't die anytime soon—

314
00:18:42,030 --> 00:18:43,590
even if he doesn't wake up right away.

315
00:18:43,590 --> 00:18:44,590
The Revival Pill.

316
00:18:52,590 --> 00:18:53,510
Do you have water?

317
00:18:53,510 --> 00:18:54,160
Water?

318
00:18:54,270 --> 00:18:56,600
Where can we get water in this wilderness?

319
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,000
What are you doing?

320
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:00,920
Administer it with human blood.

321
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:02,440
It might work even better.

322
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:03,680
No.

323
00:19:04,270 --> 00:19:05,680
Do you have a better way?

324
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:07,510
Let me do it.

325
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:16,830
Enough.

326
00:19:16,830 --> 00:19:18,030
Enough.

327
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:38,140
It seems to be working.

328
00:19:41,880 --> 00:19:42,590
Xiao Chi.

329
00:19:43,070 --> 00:19:43,830
Xiao Chi.

330
00:20:40,590 --> 00:20:41,480
You're awake.

331
00:20:41,960 --> 00:20:42,920
How do you feel?

332
00:20:43,070 --> 00:20:43,790
Much better.

333
00:20:43,790 --> 00:20:45,200
Here, drink some water.

334
00:20:56,480 --> 00:20:57,540
I feel much better.

335
00:20:59,400 --> 00:21:00,110
But,

336
00:21:00,640 --> 00:21:02,880
it would be great
if there was some wine right now.

337
00:21:02,880 --> 00:21:03,920
In your dreams.

338
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:05,350
Even for this little bit of water,

339
00:21:05,350 --> 00:21:06,440
I had to walk a long way

340
00:21:06,440 --> 00:21:07,840
to find a family to get it.

341
00:21:08,310 --> 00:21:09,830
Give it to me when you're done.

342
00:21:09,830 --> 00:21:11,690
I still need it for Mo's medicine.

343
00:21:21,510 --> 00:21:22,310
Besides,

344
00:21:22,310 --> 00:21:24,070
with your current condition,

345
00:21:24,200 --> 00:21:26,530
you couldn't drink even if there was wine.

346
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:34,830
From today on,

347
00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:36,880
I plan to treat you twice a day.

348
00:21:36,920 --> 00:21:38,780
That way, you'll recover faster.

349
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:39,270
Okay.

350
00:21:40,030 --> 00:21:40,920
Once you're better,

351
00:21:40,920 --> 00:21:42,160
I can take Mo back to Changmo

352
00:21:42,160 --> 00:21:43,160
to find Uncle Lie.

353
00:21:53,070 --> 00:21:54,200
You can't leave.

354
00:21:58,070 --> 00:21:59,070
Why?

355
00:22:01,510 --> 00:22:02,160
His...

356
00:22:02,510 --> 00:22:04,680
His case file is blank.

357
00:22:05,110 --> 00:22:06,920
And he has been locked up
in the Imperial Prison for so many years,

358
00:22:06,920 --> 00:22:08,050
tortured every day.

359
00:22:08,240 --> 00:22:09,900
There must be a hidden secret.

360
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:11,830
Then why can't I leave?

361
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:16,010
The most urgent task

362
00:22:16,510 --> 00:22:18,040
is to settle him down first.

363
00:22:20,920 --> 00:22:22,050
Then what can you do?

364
00:22:28,310 --> 00:22:29,710
I'll take you somewhere.

365
00:22:30,270 --> 00:22:31,160
Seventeen?

366
00:22:32,240 --> 00:22:33,790
Haven't seen you in so many years.

367
00:22:33,790 --> 00:22:35,200
You really haven't changed a bit.

368
00:22:35,200 --> 00:22:36,920
Seventeen has been dead for years.

369
00:22:36,920 --> 00:22:38,720
That's her daughter, Eighteen.

370
00:22:40,240 --> 00:22:41,030
Master.

371
00:22:41,830 --> 00:22:42,640
How have you been?

372
00:22:42,640 --> 00:22:43,680
You little brat.

373
00:22:43,680 --> 00:22:44,740
Who is your master?

374
00:22:45,310 --> 00:22:46,110
Why are you here?

375
00:22:46,110 --> 00:22:48,030
If you have no business,
leave immediately.

376
00:22:48,030 --> 00:22:50,550
You're kicking me out
right after I arrived?

377
00:22:50,550 --> 00:22:53,210
You usually don't come to
me with anything good.

378
00:22:55,480 --> 00:22:57,070
Who is this?

379
00:23:00,030 --> 00:23:01,310
She is Han Yunling.

380
00:23:04,030 --> 00:23:04,880
You like her.

381
00:23:05,030 --> 00:23:06,310
What are you saying?

382
00:23:06,510 --> 00:23:08,170
I don't want to know who she is.

383
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:09,720
What are you doing here?

384
00:23:09,720 --> 00:23:10,720
You have learned the martial arts,

385
00:23:10,720 --> 00:23:12,070
and I have passed
down the military books to you.

386
00:23:12,070 --> 00:23:13,310
Why are you still here?

387
00:23:13,310 --> 00:23:14,110
This time,

388
00:23:14,750 --> 00:23:16,950
I want you to help me look after someone.

389
00:23:21,510 --> 00:23:22,680
We haven't seen each other
for so many years,

390
00:23:22,680 --> 00:23:24,340
and you give me such a big gift.

391
00:23:24,510 --> 00:23:25,590
You brought a dead man here.

392
00:23:25,590 --> 00:23:26,310
What do you mean?

393
00:23:26,310 --> 00:23:27,590
He is not dead yet.

394
00:23:27,590 --> 00:23:29,310
What's the relationship between you two?

395
00:23:29,310 --> 00:23:30,400
He is my cousin.

396
00:23:30,680 --> 00:23:32,510
He has been locked up
in the Imperial Prison all these years.

397
00:23:32,510 --> 00:23:34,170
Xiao Chi helped me rescue him.

398
00:23:36,440 --> 00:23:39,400
Hey, he does still
have a little breath left.

399
00:23:40,200 --> 00:23:41,790
He is in this state right now.

400
00:23:41,790 --> 00:23:42,640
Who did this?

401
00:23:42,960 --> 00:23:43,510
It was me.

402
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:45,830
How did you do it?

403
00:23:45,830 --> 00:23:46,640
I gave him...

404
00:23:51,830 --> 00:23:53,880
If you agree to let Mo stay here,

405
00:23:54,070 --> 00:23:56,070
I'll teach you how I did it.

406
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:57,200
It's a deal.

407
00:24:00,070 --> 00:24:01,130
Within three days,

408
00:24:01,270 --> 00:24:02,790
you must find the best wine in the capital

409
00:24:02,790 --> 00:24:03,790
and bring it to me.

410
00:24:03,830 --> 00:24:05,110
If there is no good wine,

411
00:24:05,110 --> 00:24:05,920
I'll chop him up

412
00:24:05,920 --> 00:24:07,320
and feed him to Eighteen.

413
00:24:08,000 --> 00:24:10,400
Don't worry, I'll bring it
to you tomorrow.

414
00:24:10,920 --> 00:24:12,920
My father and I have
run a tavern for many years.

415
00:24:12,920 --> 00:24:14,520
Sir, don't try to deceive me.

416
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:16,520
Miss, you don't know something.

417
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:18,110
This shop

418
00:24:18,110 --> 00:24:20,160
is next to General Xiao's residence.

419
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:23,000
It's also not far from
General Xiao's garrison.

420
00:24:23,000 --> 00:24:23,790
Say no more.

421
00:24:24,590 --> 00:24:25,880
I will

422
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:27,790
rent this shop.

423
00:24:29,510 --> 00:24:30,720
You rented it just like that?

424
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:32,200
Isn't it too hasty?

425
00:24:32,720 --> 00:24:33,880
How could it be?

426
00:24:35,030 --> 00:24:35,960
Here is the rent.

427
00:24:36,790 --> 00:24:38,790
Miss, you are a straightforward person.

428
00:24:38,790 --> 00:24:40,880
Then I wish your tavern

429
00:24:41,110 --> 00:24:42,270
a prosperous business.

430
00:24:42,270 --> 00:24:43,870
Thank you for your blessing.

431
00:24:46,550 --> 00:24:49,440
Lust is a blade

432
00:24:49,880 --> 00:24:51,480
that cuts deep.

433
00:24:56,480 --> 00:24:57,160
Lord Fei.

434
00:24:57,160 --> 00:24:58,720
You are here so early.

435
00:24:59,030 --> 00:25:00,240
I agreed with your general yesterday

436
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:01,110
to move here today.

437
00:25:01,110 --> 00:25:01,920
Where is he?

438
00:25:02,590 --> 00:25:04,030
He went out yesterday during the day

439
00:25:04,030 --> 00:25:05,690
and didn't come back at night.

440
00:25:06,310 --> 00:25:07,200
He just returned to the capital,

441
00:25:07,200 --> 00:25:09,110
and he hasn't finished
his work at the residence.

442
00:25:09,110 --> 00:25:10,310
What is so important?

443
00:25:10,510 --> 00:25:11,840
I don't know about that.

444
00:25:13,590 --> 00:25:14,240
All right.

445
00:25:14,240 --> 00:25:16,510
I don't know how much
longer I have to wait for him.

446
00:25:16,510 --> 00:25:17,370
Go do your work.

447
00:25:17,550 --> 00:25:18,070
Yes.

448
00:25:20,880 --> 00:25:21,680
Zheng?

449
00:25:25,920 --> 00:25:27,320
So you're only just back?

450
00:25:27,880 --> 00:25:29,410
Where did you go last night?

451
00:25:30,680 --> 00:25:31,810
I had some business.

452
00:25:32,070 --> 00:25:33,030
Never mind.

453
00:25:33,200 --> 00:25:34,270
The child has grown up

454
00:25:34,270 --> 00:25:35,670
and can't be controlled.

455
00:25:36,590 --> 00:25:38,400
Come with me to the West Courtyard.

456
00:25:38,400 --> 00:25:39,160
West Courtyard?

457
00:25:39,160 --> 00:25:40,490
Don't just stand there.

458
00:25:47,240 --> 00:25:48,700
Why are you standing here?

459
00:25:48,720 --> 00:25:49,720
My lords.

460
00:25:49,790 --> 00:25:51,510
Her Highness is still sleeping.

461
00:25:51,510 --> 00:25:53,400
Still sleeping at this hour?

462
00:25:53,480 --> 00:25:54,920
Her Highness is of noble birth,

463
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:56,590
and the journey has been exhausting.

464
00:25:56,590 --> 00:25:58,990
She needs more sleep
to recover her energy.

465
00:25:59,510 --> 00:26:01,000
Could she not be inside?

466
00:26:04,550 --> 00:26:06,030
Her Highness is still resting.

467
00:26:06,030 --> 00:26:07,440
If you dare to overstep your bounds,

468
00:26:07,440 --> 00:26:09,240
don't blame me for how I respond.

469
00:26:09,310 --> 00:26:11,640
Jin Xi, let them in.
